quirking slightly in some form of repressed humor, &quot;Ahh yess, you seek
a protoform, a blank cybertronain, upon which you can imprint anything
you like.&quot;

Shaking his head Cryotek smiles coldly, &quot;You ask for much and yet you
have brought nothing to give.&quot; Cryotek opened his hand as he gestured
to Hydras, &quot;Yet I offer you much, a base and your men, and yet you
refused.&quot;

Cryotek tilts his head, as if confused by Hydras, &quot;Why should I give
you what you are asking for? I may have my own plans with them.&quot;

